      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEADLY COOL (1) looks close to another win after finishing second from Box 6 last time (34.56) at Sandown. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Good form should continue. POUND KEEPING (3) made contact with another runner and could manage only a distant seventh (30.47) in a Grade 3/4 over 520m at Wentworth Park. Can measure up this time. ZIPPING FIYERO (7) is generally an honest type in the frame at nine of 21 starts but missed the placings last time when fifth (27.48) over 485m at Horsham. Form here at this distance is sound. Has a good overall strike-rate and can find the frame here. PAW STELLA (2) impressed in her quick 29.49 win last time. Looks an each way chance.",
